high_descs: turn around and walk over to the white kitchen table
grab the spoon off of the table
turn around and walk over to the stove top
place the spoon in the pan on the back left burner
pick up the pan you put the spoon in
turn to face the bottom kitchen cabinets on your left
place the pan inside the far right bottom cabinet
anns.task_desc: place a pan with a spoon in it inside the kitchen cabinet

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the table and chair in the far right of the room
Pick up the ladle that's on the table
Turn back around and take the ladle over to the stove
Place the ladle in the black frying pan that's on the back left stove burner
Pick up the frying pan with the ladle in it
Turn to your left and look at the bottom row of cabinets in front of you
Place the frying pan and ladle in the bottom right cabinet
anns.task_desc: Putting a ladle with a frying pan away into a cabinet

high_descs: You will have to turn left and cross the room and turn left as well.
You have to reach the white round table in order to pick up the  spoon.
Turn left twice and than to the right.
Facing the bowl on top of the stove and drop in the spoon.
With the two together in hand twist in place
Open the cabin door at the bottom , on the left.
Drop the two in and close the door.
anns.task_desc: To find two important tools , one from the main area location while the other hidden with care.
